From: "Wulfric Rennison" <wulftech@...>
To: <EverQuest@yahoogroups.com>
Sent: Tuesday, October 14, 2003 12:56 PM
Subject: [EverQuest] Looking for a weblink


I feel kinda stupid asking this.

One day while sitting in class ignoring my professor's lecture, I was
browsing the web and came across a weblink. It was a series of comic strips
based on EverQuest that I thought was really well done. I had intended on
posting the link to this list, but never did. Now I'm trying to find the
link again but I cant remember how or where I found it. So I was hoping
that maybe someone here might know what I'm talking about. Essentially the
comic strip starts out with a female wood elf turning in her quest paper to
become a druid, but some things happen and she ends up being taken under the
wing (?) of an Iksar who was a friend of her father. The Iksar character is
named after the person's character who draws the strip. Hopefully this is
enough information that someone might recognize it and post the link.

Thanks in advance.

Wulfric
